pageProduct.name: PAW Rosearoma Groom Mist 125ml
pageProduct.description:
General Information

PAW Rose Aroma Grooming Mist is a gentle alcohol free grooming spray to freshen the coat between washes. It is great for revitalising and de-tangling the coat, making grooming easy.

Common Uses

pH balanced, alcohol free and formulated to be compatible to pets’ skin. Gentle smoothing and detangling agents for a silky soft coat. Rich moisturising ingredients for coat health & skin nutrients to add body and shine. Natural essential oils of rose water for a fresh pure scent

Ingredients

Purified water, cetearyl alcohol, glycerin (vegetable), surfactant, avocado oil, jojoba oil, preservative, thickener, vitamin E, rose oil, patchouli oil, Australian sandalwood oil.
